\begin_layout Title
Thinking about the Space of Irrationals Topologically
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Let 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{R}$
\end_inset

 denote the real number line and 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 denote the set of all irrational numbers.
 The irrational numbers and the set 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 occupy an important place in mathematics.
 The set 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 with the Euclidean topology inherited from the full real line is a topological
 space in its own right.
 Thus the space 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 has some of the same properties inherited from the Euclidean real line,
 e.g., just to name a few, it is hereditarily separable, hereditarily Lindelof,
 paracompact and metrizable.
 The space of the irrational numbers 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 has many properties apart from the full real line (e.g.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 is totally disconnected).
 In this post, we look at a topological description of the space 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
将无理数集记为 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

, 无理数拓扑继承自实数集 
\begin_inset Formula $\RR$
\end_inset

 的通常拓扑, 仍用符号 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 来记这个拓扑空间.
 无理数空间 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 有一些性质继承于实拓扑空间, 比如它有遗传可分性, 遗传 Lindelof 性质, 仿紧性和可度量化的, 也有一些性质是实拓扑空间不具有的,
 比如全不连通性.
 下面对无理数空间 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 进行一些拓扑方面的论述.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Let 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

 be the set of all nonnegative integers.
 Then the space 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 of irrational numbers is topologically equivalent (i.e.
 homeomorphic to) the product space 
\begin_inset Formula $\prod\limits _{i=0}^{\infty}X_{i}$
\end_inset

 where each 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{i}=\omega$
\end_inset

 has the discrete topology.
 We will also denote the product space 
\begin_inset Formula $\prod\limits _{i=0}^{\infty}X_{i}$
\end_inset

 by 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

.
 We have the following theorem.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
设 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

 是非负整数集.
 则无理数空间 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 拓扑等价于乘积空间 
\begin_inset Formula $\prod\limits _{i=0}^{\infty}X_{i}$
\end_inset

, 其中 
\begin_inset Formula $X_{i}=\omega$
\end_inset

 并配有离散拓扑.
 为方便起见, 将 
\begin_inset Formula $\prod\limits _{i=0}^{\infty}X_{i}$
\end_inset

 简记为 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

.
 则有如下定理
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
The space 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 of irrational numbers is homeomorphic to the product space 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Because of this theorem, we can look at irrational numbers as sequences
 of nonnegative integers.
 Specifically each irrational number can be identified by a unique sequence
 of nonnegative integers.
 We can think of each such unique sequence as an address to locate an irrational
 number.
 In the remainder of the post, we describe at a high level how to define
 the unique addresses, which will also give us a homeomorphic map between
 the space 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 and the product space 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
这个定理告诉我们, 可以将无理数集看成非负整数集中的序列.
 实际上, 每个无理数可以唯一地对应一个非负整数序列, 下面将给出这种一一对应的构造, 并且证明这个映射实际上是同胚映射.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
