\begin_layout Standard
记所有有理数序列为 
\begin_inset Formula $r_{0},r_{1},r_{2},r_{3},\cdots$
\end_inset

, 其中 
\begin_inset Formula $r_{0}=0$
\end_inset

.
 将实直线分成可数个互不交叠的区间, 并记为 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{0}=[0,1]$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{1}=[-1,0]$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{2}=[1,2]$
\end_inset

, ...
 如上图所示.
 将每个区间简单地记为 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i}=[L_{i},R_{i}]$
\end_inset

, 其中 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{i},R_{i}$
\end_inset

 分别为区间 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i}$
\end_inset

 的左右端点.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Step 1
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In each of the interval 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i}$
\end_inset

, we further divide it into non-overlapping intervals.
 The left endpoint and the right endpoint of the interval 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i}$
\end_inset

 are 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{i}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $R_{i}$
\end_inset

, respectively.
 We choose a sequence 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i,0},x_{i,1},x_{i,2},\cdots$
\end_inset

 of rational numbers converging to the right endpoint 
\begin_inset Formula $R_{i}$
\end_inset

.
 Then let 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,0}=[L_{i},x_{i,0}]$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,1}=[x_{i,0},x_{i,1}]$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,2}=[x_{i,1},x_{i,2}]$
\end_inset

, etc (see the following figure).
\end_layout

