\begin_layout Standard
Two important points to consider in Step 1.
 One is that we make sure the rational number 
\begin_inset Formula $r_{1}$
\end_inset

 is chosen as an endpoint of some interval in Step 1.
 The second is that the length of each 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,j}$
\end_inset

 is less than 
\begin_inset Formula ${\displaystyle \frac{1}{2^{1}}}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
进一步将每个区间划分为不交叠的子区间, 如区间 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i}=[L_{i},R_{i}]$
\end_inset

 , 取 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i}$
\end_inset

 中收敛于 
\begin_inset Formula $R_{i}$
\end_inset

 的有理数序列 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i,0},x_{i,1},x_{i,2},\cdots$
\end_inset

, 并将 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i}$
\end_inset

 划分为区间 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,0}=[L_{i},x_{i,0}]$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,1}=[x_{i,0},x_{i,1}]$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,2}=[x_{i,1},x_{i,2}]$
\end_inset

, ...
 如上图所示.
 需要注意是, 在上面的区间划分中, 有理数 
\begin_inset Formula $r_{1}$
\end_inset

 必须被所在的某个区间 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i}$
\end_inset

 的有理数序列选中, 并且每一个有理数序列的选择都必须保证 
\begin_inset Formula $\left|A_{i,j}\right|<\frac{1}{2^{1}}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Step 2 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In each of the interval 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,j}$
\end_inset

, we further divide it into non-overlapping intervals.
 The left endpoint and the right endpoint of the interval 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,j}$
\end_inset

 are 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{i,j}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $R_{i,j}$
\end_inset

, respectively.
 We choose a sequence 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{i,j,0},x_{i,j,1},x_{i,j,2},\cdots$
\end_inset

 of rational numbers converging to the left endpoint 
\begin_inset Formula $L_{i,j}$
\end_inset

.
 Then let 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,j,0}=[x_{i,j,0},R_{i,j}]$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,j,1}=[x_{i,j,1},x_{i,j,0}]$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{i,j,2}=[x_{i,j,2},x_{i,j,1}]$
