\begin_layout Subsection
Remark
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In the process described above, the endpoints of the intervals 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{f(0),\cdots,f(n)}$
\end_inset

 are rational numbers and we make sure that all the rational numbers are
 used as endpoints.
 We also make sure that the intervals from the successive steps are nested
 closed intervals with lengths 
\begin_inset Formula $\rightarrow0$
\end_inset

.
 The consequence of this point is that the nested decreasing closed intervals
 will collapse to one single point (since the real line is a complete metric
 space) and this single point must be an irrational number (since all the
 rational numbers are used up as endpoints of the nested closed intervals).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
如此继续划分下去, 将得到以有理数为端点的区间 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{f(0),\cdots,f(n)}$
\end_inset

, 并且在构造过程中, 所有的有理数都被用于某个区间的端点.
 随着序列 
\begin_inset Formula $f(0),\cdots,f(n),\cdots$
\end_inset

 的延伸, 区间 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{f(0),\cdots,f(n)}$
\end_inset

 形成一个闭区间套, 这个闭区间套收敛于一点, 这个点是一个无理数.
 (证明如下)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
In Step 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 where 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 is an odd integer, we make the endpoints of the new intervals converge
 to the right.
 In Step 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 where 
\begin_inset Formula $i>1$
\end_inset

 is an even integer, we make the endpoints of the new intervals converge
 to the left.
 This manipulation is to ensure that the nested closed intervals will never
 share the same endpoint from one step all the way to the end of the process.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
实际上, 在第 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 步, 当 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 是奇数时, 所构造的区间端点都收敛于右端点; 当 
\begin_inset Formula $i$
\end_inset

 是偶数时, 区间端点都收敛于左端点.
 由于区间端点在收敛过程中的极限总是不可达的, 所以任何区间套不可能收敛到某个子区间的端点.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Thus if we have 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

, then 
\begin_inset Formula $\bigcap\limits _{n=0}^{\infty}A_{f(0),\cdots,f(n)}\ne\varnothing$
\end_inset

 and in fact has only one point that is an irrational number.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
因此, 如果 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

, 则 
\begin_inset Formula $\bigcap\limits _{n=0}^{\infty}A_{f(0),\cdots,f(n)}\ne\varnothing$
\end_inset

 且恰好包含一个无理数作为元素.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
On the other hand, for each point 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

, we can locate inductively a sequence of intervals, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{f(0)}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{f(0),f(1)}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{f(0),f(1),f(2)}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\cdots$
\end_inset

, containing the point 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

.
 This sequence of nested closed intervals must collapse to a single point
 and the single point must be the irrational number 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
另一方面, 对于任意的点 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

, 可以递归的定位出一个区间序列 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{f(0)}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{f(0),f(1)}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{f(0),f(1),f(2)}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\cdots$
\end_inset

 包含点 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

.
 这个区间列恰是收敛于 
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

 的区间套.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The process described above gives us a one-to-one mapping from 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 onto the product space 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

.
 This mapping is also continuous in both directions, making it a homeomorphism.
 the nested intervals defined above form a base for the Euclidean topology
 on 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

.
 These basic open sets have a natural correspondance with basic open sets
 in the product space 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
以上构造过程给出了从 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 到乘积空间 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

 的一个双射.
 这个映射是连续的, 且是一个同胚映射.
 上面构造的闭区间全体组成的集合给出了 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 上的一个拓扑基.
 这些开集对应于乘积拓扑 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

 上的开集.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
For example, for 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ A_{f(0),\cdots,f(n)}\cap\mathbb{P}:n\in\omega\right\} $
\end_inset

 is a local base at the point 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in\bigcap\limits _{n=0}^{\infty}A_{f(0),\cdots,f(n)}$
\end_inset

.
 On the other hand, each 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{f(0),\cdots,f(n)}\cap\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 has a natural counterpart in a basic open set in the product space, namely
 the following set:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\{ g\in\omega^{\omega}:g\restriction n=f\restriction n\right\} .
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The above process establishes that the countable product of the integers,
 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

, is equivalent topologically to the Euclidean space 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
例如, 对于 
\begin_inset Formula $f\in\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\left\{ A_{f(0),\cdots,f(n)}\cap\mathbb{P}:n\in\omega\right\} $
\end_inset

 是点 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in\bigcap\limits _{n=0}^{\infty}A_{f(0),\cdots,f(n)}$
\end_inset

 处的一个局部基.
 另一方面, 每个点集 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{f(0),\cdots,f(n)}\cap\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 与乘积空间 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

 中的基本开集对应, 也就是 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

 中的如下开集:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left\{ g\in\omega^{\omega}:g\restriction n=f\restriction n\right\} .
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
即得 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 与 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega^{\omega}$
\end_inset

 之间的拓扑等价关系.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Theorem
设 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}=\RR\setminus\QQ$
\end_inset

 是继承了 
\begin_inset Formula $\RR$
\end_inset

 的通常拓扑的子拓扑空间, 
\begin_inset Formula $\NN$
\end_inset

 是配有离散拓扑的空间, 则 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbb{P}$
\end_inset

 与乘积拓扑 
\begin_inset Formula $\NN^{\NN}\coloneqq\prod_{i\in\NN}\NN$
\end_inset

 同胚.
\end_layout

